                <note rend="inline" type="source">791.003/145: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Philip</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-07-06T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 6, 1928—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>56. Your 67, July 6, 6 a.m. Text as modified is satisfactory. You may sign and
                    exchange notes.<note n="56" xml:id="d637fn56">The Minister reported in telegram
                        No. 72, July 11: “Notes providing for Provisional Agreement in matters of
                        personal status and family law jurisdiction signed and exchanged today.”
                        (File No. 791.003/147.)</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
